Actions.Text: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS
COMMITTEE DISCHARGED AND COMMITTED TO RULES

Title: Relates to the use of property in a land bank for community gardens
Summary: Permits a land bank prioritize the use of property for a community garden.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the not-for-profit corporation law, in relation to the use of property in a land bank for the creation of a community garden
